{"tid":1814030,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"『26』改咗喉嘅入黎","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T23:25:06.000Z","uid":99819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eab9965742ea670f9a14308d48e8bfb4198e424c","tid":1814030,"uid":99819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"小弟揸緊17年R6想問下有無同樣揸緊R6嘅師兄能夠分享下。<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟想改蠍子喉，但心大心細緊全梳定尾段。<br />\n-全梳（Racing Line）  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Yf2LDy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Yf2LDy.jpg&h=0f98ec85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油耗高左 係我其中一個憂慮嘅問題，因為係腳車 唔想一下子油耗調升。<br />\n<br />\n-尾段   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A4ySiE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4A4ySiE.jpg&h=d6019069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nR6中段個便當化晒啲聲，驚淨改尾段同原廠喉把聲無乜分別。<br />\n<br />\n🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍🏍"},{"pid":"e412c322db6360c65f2db7f30dec50ed54729452","tid":1814030,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"全啦<br />\n你r6油錢都唔差果小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28be8a6b8082d3e238b3138df3520d4dd5f191d5","tid":1814030,"uid":61367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔好改慳番"},{"pid":"a8c01ae5b71389e955f762742162913e7c474e62","tid":1814030,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"R6做腳 仲同我計較油錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c8a886c531a4410cdd14b44c777d639595c6a0","tid":1814030,"uid":99819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"所以想聽下咁多位師兄嘅意見。"},{"pid":"fa594017961f7913f82ba3745ec448b45bc164dd","tid":1814030,"uid":62412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"出部r6做腳車係咩心態，油錢都唔爭嗰少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj